org.gvsig.topology.ui
Interface ITopologyContentProvider

public interface ITopologyContentProvider

All classes that implements this interface could provide the needed content to create a topology:

  • vectorial layers
  • a view's map context.
  • topology rules.
A panel where the user is entering its options, or even a topology could provides this info. Implementation classes are useful to connect the GUI with the model (Topology, user entries, etc.)

Alvaro Zabala
